Description:
The Blazor interns are at it again! Come check out the cool new features that superstar Blazor intern, Roland Vizner, has been hard at work on this summer, including a new component for handling images and other media files. We'll also take a look at the new state persistence support for Blazor enhanced navigation.

Community Links: https://www.theurlist.com/blazor-standup-20250909

Featuring: Daniel Roth, Javier Calvarro Nelson, Roland Vizner

#dotnet #aspnetcore
